Data Attributes
data-url
    contains the url of the document.(ex: almuallim://TheHolyQuran?chapter=1&verse=1&className=org.almuallim.theholyquran.api.OpenChapter)
     javascript code to retrieve the url
        
        $('#document').data('url');

data-chapter-index (module specific - The Holy Quran)
    contains the chapter index 

    $('#document').data('chapter-index');

data-url
     contains the url for an article(verse) in the document
     javascript code to retrieve the url for selected article(verse)
        
        $('article.selected').data('url');

data-verse-index (module specific - The Holy Quran)
    contains the verse index
    
data-ref
    contains the ref text example(Chapter 6: Verse 1)
data-translator-id
    
data-translated-lang